==制作==
2012年10月，《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志报道，卡洛斯·沙尔丹哈已与[[20世纪福斯|20世纪福斯]]签订了五年的合约，以拍摄动画电影和真人电影，本片就是其中一部 <ref>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title='Rio' helmer Carlos Saldanha inks Fox pact|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/rio-helmer-carlos-saldanha-inks-fox-pact-1118061241/|accessdate=October 26, 2012|newspaper=Variety|date=October 25, 2012|archivedate=2009-06-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630013226/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/rio-helmer-carlos-saldanha-inks-fox-pact-1118061241/|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。前作编剧{{link-en|唐·雷莫|Don Rhymer}}于2012年11月28日因[[头颈癌|头颈癌]]逝世享年51岁，当时他正在为本片写剧本<ref>{{cite news|title=Screenwriter Don Rhymer dies at 51|date=December 3, 2012|url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/screenwriter-don-rhymer-dies-at-51-1118063010/|accessdate=February 21, 2014|newspaper=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630013226/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/screenwriter-don-rhymer-dies-at-51-1118063010/|archivedate=2009-06-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2013年4月18日，影片的初版[[预告片|预告片]]在[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]的动漫影展上正式发布<ref>{{cite news|last=Lesnick|first=Silas|title=20th Century Fox Previews Its 2013 Slate|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/cinemaconnews.php?id=103174|accessdate=April 25, 2013|work=Comingsoon.net|date=April 18, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929190240/http://collider.com/rodrigo-santoro-senna-300-rise-of-an-empire-interview/222104/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，5月14日同款预告片在网络上发行<ref>{{cite news|last=Jardine|first=William|title=Watch: Portuguese Teaser for Rio 2|date=May 14, 2013|accessdate=May 15, 2013|url=http://www.a113animation.com/2013/05/watch-spanish-teaser-for-rio-2.html|newspaper=A113Animation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630013226/http://www.a113animation.com/2013/05/watch-spanish-teaser-for-rio-2.html|archivedate=2009-06-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

